11. Valāhakavagga Kumbhasutta ^n103 “Cattārome, bhikkhave, kumbhā. 
Katame cattāro? 
Tuccho pihito, 
pūro vivaṭo, 
tuccho vivaṭo, 
pūro pihito—
Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro kumbhā. 
